<br>
The epic cons green at lvl 65.<br>
<br>
There is no soloing post 60 for the most part.<br>
<br>
The new pets are better then epic.<br>
a) Air Pet mitigates damage better and with summoned gear gets close to epic hps.<br>
b) Water Pet blows Epic damage away. It isn't even close once you get all the summoned items and new burnout.<br>
c) The new buffs/items do not augment the epic pet in the same way they do the new pets. Burnout 5 from what I can see doesn't do much for the epic pet while it has dramatic affects on the new pets.<br>
d) add in the fact that new pets can hit all mobs with procs. My pet was nuking AoW with ease.<br>
<br>
Basically the mage epic has been made useless. We still do not have a all around pet that totally out does the epic but the truth is with soloing dead there is little need for a great all around pet. In a group you will be using air and water. I have epic and hardly ever use it. The new pets are just better.<br>
